"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-08-04-Why-do-swimmers-wear-down-jackets-at-the-Olympics--1vNw5EsnEXe-p.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 145, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can change your cookie settings through your browser.\", \"from\": 146, \"to\": 203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gong Zhe  Copied  Chinese swimmers before the women's 4x200m freestyle relay, Paris, France, August 1, 2024.\", \"from\": 205, \"to\": 313, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 283, \"end\": 288, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999990961018277, \"rank\": 9.038989620781455e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 290, \"end\": 296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9535039140482313, \"rank\": 0.047802286559465806, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  Chinese swimming prodigy Pan Zhanle made a splash at the Paris Olympics after snatching gold in the men's 100m freestyle and smashing his own world record.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 475, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 320, \"end\": 327, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6761618749490144, \"rank\": 0.4786825547112669, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But eagle-eyed viewers noticed something peculiar: Pan entered the venue sporting a down jacket!\", \"from\": 476, \"to\": 572, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Social media in China buzzed with curiosity, with posts on Weibo, one of the country's most popular platforms, exceeding 10 million views on the topic.\", \"from\": 574, \"to\": 725, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 590, \"end\": 595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9999961112883406, \"rank\": 1.9053498746708286e-06, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\", \"score\": 0.9999405942134592, \"rank\": 5.9324582404458126e-05, \"text\": \"Weibo\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A Weibo poll revealed some hilarious guesses.\", \"from\": 727, \"to\": 772, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 729, \"end\": 734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\", \"score\": 0.9999405942134592, \"rank\": 5.9324582404458126e-05, \"text\": \"Weibo\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sina_Weibo\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly 7,000 accounts voted for the rational \\\"staying warm\\\" option, but a few hundred opted for \\\"shyness\\\" or \\\"looking cool.\\\"\", \"from\": 773, \"to\": 897, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"As it turned out, the jacket is indeed for warmth.\", \"from\": 898, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pan Zhanle of Team China before the men's 100m freestyle semifinal during the Summer Olympic Games in Paris, France, July 30, 2024.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1081, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1052, \"end\": 1057, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999990961018277, \"rank\": 9.038989620781455e-07, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9535039140482313, \"rank\": 0.047802286559465806, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"/CFP  \\\"Swimmers often face long waits between warm-up and competition,\\\" Zou Rongqi of China's General Administration of Sport explained to Science and Technology Daily in late 2023.\", \"from\": 1082, \"to\": 1263, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Muscle temperature could sometimes dictate performance, so jackets are essential to maintain warmth, even in summer.\\\"\", \"from\": 1264, \"to\": 1382, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Also, down jackets are lightweight and easy to take off, perfect for pre-swimming preparation,\\\" Zou added.\", \"from\": 1384, \"to\": 1491, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1481, \"end\": 1484, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoucheng\", \"score\": 0.6805181707914357, \"rank\": 0.44014868766710796, \"text\": \"Zou\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoucheng\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zoucheng\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This sentiment was echoed by Professor Su Hao from Beijing Sport University.\", \"from\": 1493, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1544, \"end\": 1568, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Sport_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.7540420256946586e-14, \"text\": \"Beijing Sport University\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Sport_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beijing_Sport_University\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Down jackets are soft and will not restrict warm-up exercises.\\\"\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For amateur swimmers considering a down jacket purchase, Su clarified to the Chinese newspaper Global Times that it's unnecessary for indoor pools.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1783, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1713, \"end\": 1720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.6761618749490144, \"rank\": 0.4786825547112669, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1731, \"end\": 1743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_Times\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Global Times\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_Times\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Global_Times\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, a down jacket can be great after swimming outdoors, especially in winter.\", \"from\": 1784, \"to\": 1866, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You do not have to wear a down jacket.\", \"from\": 1868, \"to\": 1907, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A thick bath blanket is enough,\\\" Su said.\", \"from\": 1908, \"to\": 1949, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 1951, \"to\": 2211, \"entities\": []}]}"